title: Trailer Wiring Install: CURT 56183 on 2008 Dodge Nitro
description:
This video depicts the installation of the CURT 56183 T-Connector on a 2008 Dodge Nitro.

Install Sheet - https://www.curtmfg.com/masterlibrary/56183/installsheet/CME_56183_INS.PDF

Application Coverage:
2007-2011 Dodge Nitro 
2008-2012 Jeep Liberty 

Special Notes:
WARNING!
Verify miscellaneous items that may be hidden 
behind or under any surface before drilling to 
avoid damage and/or personal injury.

Warning:
-This video is intended to be used as reference. Please refer to print instructions for complete installation information.
